  "doc_id": "36048",
  "text": "Caltech-UCSD Birds-200-2011 (CUB-200) [CITATION_1] is an image dataset with 200 bird species and a total of 11,788 images. It also has the annotations for 15 part locations, 312 binary attributes, and one bounding box per image. However, these attributes are not used in this work as the design of the proposed model is not suitable for multi-label problem in its current state. Hence, the ArtGAN-AEM is trained based on the 200 bird species classes.",
